<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Their rekindled romance has been going from strength-to-strength.</p>

<p>And Yazmin Oukhellou and James Lock looked smitten as they stepped out for dinner together at Sexy Fish in Mayfair, London, on Tuesday.</p>

<p>The TOWIE stars, aged 26 and 33, were seen holding hands as they strolled to the trendy eatery for their night out.</p>

<p>Smitten: TOWIE's Yazmin Oukhellou put on a loved-up display with on-again beau James Lock as they held hands while heading out for dinner in Mayfair, London, on Tuesday</p>

<p>Yaz put on a busty display in a plunging black Fendi jumpsuit that fit snugly on her slender frame and featured a semi-sheer belt to accentuate her waist. </p>

<p>She boosted her height in a pair of open-toe heels, and she kept her personal items in a small clutch bag.</p>

<p>The reality star wore her raven tresses in a sleek, straight style that fell over her shoulders, and she used a light palette of make-up for the occasion.</p>

<p>James matched his girlfriend's fashion choices, as he tucked in a short-sleeved black shirt into a pair of matching slacks. </p>

<p>Wow! Yaz put on a busty display in a plunging black Fendi jumpsuit that fit snugly on her slender frame</p>

<p>Stylish: Yaz boosted her height in a pair of open-toe heels, and she kept her personal items in a small clutch bag</p>

<p>Dapper: James matched his girlfriend's fashion choices, as he tucked in a short-sleeved black shirt into a pair of matching slacks</p>

<p>Yazmin had dumped Lockie over claims he had cheated on her while they were on a romantic holiday together in Turkey, and has said she still doesn't trust him but wouldn't say 'no' if he popped the question.</p>

<p>Speaking to The Sun, the brunette beauty said: 'We are trying to take things really slow but I know what I am like.  </p>

<p>'I do love him and if he did propose to me I would say yes and marry him. I still don't trust him but I do trust him more this time, which is strange because he messed up. But I do believe he has changed.'</p>

<p>Yazmin also revealed that the couple are now having weekly therapy sessions via Zoom after starting during lockdown, which is helping get their broken relationship back on track. </p>

<p>She added that her family and friends around her are still sceptical about the reunion but that she needs to 'prove everyone wrong'.</p>

<p>Soon after lockdown travel restrictions were lifted, Yazmin and James, who were together for two years, were seen kissing at a beach club in Mallorca.</p>

